<div class="page-body about-page">
  <section class="about-section">
    <h1>About This Project</h1>
    <p>This site lists dog breeds with images and reviews, to help future or current
    dog owners figure out which breed suits them based on personality and ease of care.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>Data Sources</h2>

    <h3>Dog CEO API</h3>
    <p>The breed list endpoint gives every real dog breed name, which is stored in the
    breeds table. The breed images endpoint gives a real photo of each breed, stored as
    an image URL on the same table.</p>

    <h3>Faker Gem</h3>
    <p>Faker generates all of the review data, including the reviewer names, ratings,
    comments, and the three trait scores for playfulness, affection, and ease of care.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>Groups</h2>
    <div class="group-row">
      <% Group.all.each do |group| %>
        <div class="group-chip"><%= group.name %></div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>Database Structure</h2>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>Groups</h3>
        <table class="table about-table">
          <tr><th>Type</th><th>Column</th></tr>
          <tr><td>integer (PK)</td><td>id</td></tr>
          <tr><td>string</td><td>name</td></tr>
          <tr><td>timestamp</td><td>created_at</td></tr>
          <tr><td>timestamp</td><td>updated_at</td></tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>Breeds</h3>
        <table class="table about-table">
          <tr><th>Type</th><th>Column</th></tr>
          <tr><td>integer (PK)</td><td>id</td></tr>
          <tr><td>string</td><td>name</td></tr>
          <tr><td>string</td><td>image_url</td></tr>
          <tr><td>integer (FK)</td><td>group_id</td></tr>
          <tr><td>timestamp</td><td>created_at</td></tr>
          <tr><td>timestamp</td><td>updated_at</td></tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>Reviews</h3>
        <table class="table about-table">
          <tr><th>Type</th><th>Column</th></tr>
          <tr><td>integer (PK)</td><td>id</td></tr>
          <tr><td>string</td><td>reviewer_name</td></tr>
          <tr><td>integer</td><td>rating</td></tr>
          <tr><td>text</td><td>comment</td></tr>
          <tr><td>integer</td><td>playfulness</td></tr>
          <tr><td>integer</td><td>affection</td></tr>
          <tr><td>integer</td><td>ease_of_care</td></tr>
          <tr><td>integer (FK)</td><td>breed_id</td></tr>
          <tr><td>timestamp</td><td>created_at</td></tr>
          <tr><td>timestamp</td><td>updated_at</td></tr>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>A group has many breeds, and a breed has many reviews.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>Entity Relationship Diagram</h2>
    <%= image_tag "Intro_To_Rails_Dog_Breeds_ERD.png", alt: "Dog Breeds ERD", class: "about-erd" %>
  </section>
</div>